# Start Here — Clone This Repo

1. Open your terminal
2. Go to your Projects folder:
   cd ~/Desktop/Projects
3. Clone this repository:
   git clone 
4. Move into the folder:
   cd learn-Git-Basics
5. See what's inside:
   ls

You should see: README.md, students.txt, examples/, challenges/

✅ If you see those files — you're ready for Challenge 1!
